 -check boxes can now a third Status next to "crossed"
 / "not crossed" have: If the  flag CHECKED
 is placed, but not SELECTED, will(_be) the  Checkbox with
 a Punktmuster stuffed ("Tristate-Button"). To the management
 serves the  procedure 'rsc_tristate' from EXTENDED.LST.
 The  object may be not SELECTABLE, but TOUCHEXIT.

 23.01.94 -Becomes 'rsc_load' as\than number of the object trees -1 pass/ed,
