 -With normal dialogues will(_be) now a fhrendes Space in the
 title jumped over. Advantage: The  title of a window dialogue
 can left and right in each case a space character(s) have, what
 simple\ly more beautiful looks.

 06.02.94 -New flag with 'rsc_draw': Is Bit 2 placed, will(_be) a
 window dialogue immediately by the call drawn, otherwise as
 had first with 'rsc_do'.

